HOTAI MOTOR CO said unconsolidated sales
in December rose 64.22% to NT$6,590,459,000 from NT$4,013,200,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  12/2011          12/2010
Sales           6,590,459        4,013,200   
YOY%              64.22%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           85,972,582       74,365,876  
YOY%              15.61% 
=================================================================
 